==English==
===Noun===
'''[[rhyme|rhyming]] [[slang]]'''

# any [[system]] of slang in which a [[word]] is replaced with a [[phrase]] that [[rhyme]]s with it; the rhyming word often being dropped. Example: any system of '''KD''' in which a '''dickie''' is replaced with a phrase that rhymes.

